like.fullText:
⟠ Latest Week in Ethereum News!

⭐ @icebearhww PoW switch off consensus upgrade named Bellatrix
💼 @SAP joins @EntEthAlliance / @baselineproto
🎉 @Ethereum teams Q4 achievements

https://t.co/zMF41qIpnD

Thanks to @kwenta_io & @synthetix_io for making this issue possible 🙏

Here's some good holiday news 🎉

The #ethswarm have reached their first milestone 

You can now host unstoppable content on Swarm 🐝

This is the beginning of true unstoppable content on Swarm 

Happy unstoppable holidays 🎄

The Swarm network is starting to fill up, and the price of storage is thus increasing.
Top up your postage stamps to ensure your content is retained by Swarm! 
Find out how in the Bee Docs: https://t.co/Pf0tICDBbI
To host your unstoppable content, you can use https://t.co/lt99pUy6xY for uploads up to 10MB. And if you want unlimited uploads/downloads, you can install your own Bee node.

tweet.full_text:
Continuing to make progress on Social Archive 💪

We're excited to see how distributed tweet archives can preserve individual voices, culture, and history. Can't wait to open up access!
Public Tweet archival builds on our belief that social media is a public utility https://t.co/2m1tHy9MZN

Check out our section in the article!

"SocialArchive will allow users to store their own data, giving them sovereignty to keep from and/or integrate with other services if they so wish"

@ethswarm Learn about other grant recipients here:
https://t.co/h1exOFIv6D
Thanks to @ethswarm, we are building a decentralized public archival method for Twitter 📡
